    -- Cycles have equal number of M and M' edges.
    -- Paths can be M-M, M'-M', or Mixed.
    -- M-M paths have |M| = |M'| + 1.
    -- Mixed paths have |M| = |M'|.
    -- M'-M' paths have |M'| = |M| + 1.
